.claude/
docs2/

/target/
# Catch ad-hoc target dirs used for split-profile installs / FSV release builds
# (see docs/dev-host-hygiene.md release-build recipe).
/target-*/
**/*.rs.bk

.idea/
.vscode/
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
*.iml

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

.env
.env.*
!.env.example

synapse.log
crashes/

*.snap.new
*.pending-snap
tracing-*.log

# Ephemeral FSV / operator-run output (see docs/dev-host-hygiene.md).
# Canonical locations are `.runs/<id>/` and `%LOCALAPPDATA%\synapse\runs\`;
# `fsv-<NNN>/` is a legacy pattern that should not accumulate at the repo root.
/*.log
/*.ndjson
/.runs/
/fsv-*/

# Criterion/critcmp benchmark exports are regenerated and stored off-tree.
/bench_results/

